{"type":null,"faqId":44330,"title":"POP3或IMAP类型邮箱配置过程","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>配置过程中可以先找公司的邮件管理员获取帮助及相关登录信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>选择“其他”，输入电子邮箱地址、密码等基本信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157821\" style=\"width:3.34375in;height:2.8020833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>点击“下一步”（自动配置邮箱接收设置），或点击“手动设置”进入接收协议设置页面手动完成邮箱接收发送设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157822\" style=\"width:5.7569447in;height:2.1784723in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>完成邮箱接收发送设置后，下一步确认邮件查收频率等选项。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157823\" style=\"width:1.4583334in;height:2.8020833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>设置邮箱账户名称，完成邮箱配置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=157824\" style=\"width:3.2708333in;height:2.78125in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9830","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400464000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"怎么配置,怎么设置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}